snippet.textDisplay:
Kevan Tenu Main Dikhawa
Dilon Russ Gayi Aan Chhawa
*Teri Yaadan ‘Ch Vikhra Main,*
*Duniya Se Jaava.* 

*Sunn Ve, Main Kithe Jaava?*
*Hun Chhup Gaye’aan Raahwan.* 

*Main Te Dassiya Si,*
*Khwaban Vich Takya Si.*
*Le Hun Din Vi Nahi Chadeya,*
*Te Dil Vich Tu.*
*Mere Mann Vich Tu.*
*Jadon Vi Nahi Hondi Paas,*
*Te Tadapdi Ae Rooh.* 

Tu Hi Hai Mera Naseeb
*Rahvi Tu Kareeb Sohni.*
*Haale Na Tu Ja,*
*Kadi Vi Na Jaavin Door.* 

*Assi La Ditte Jinne Vi Tu,*
*Mangdi Ae Taare.*
*Meri Jaan, Kadi Vi,*
*Na Darri Mere Pyare.* 

Dil ‘Ch Tu, Hasrat Ae Tu
*Dil ‘Ch Tu, Meri Hasrat Ae Tu.*
*Assi Tere Utte Marde Ne,*
*Mande Nahi Kyun.* 

*Hun Te Roz Tenu Chaahde Chaahde,*
*Tere Husn Utte Marde.*
*Assi Roz Ki Kariye, Sajna Bol?* 

Nachde Saare
*Haan, Tere Hi Jhol Utte Nachde Saare.*
*Tere Pyaar ‘Ch Kariye Ki?*
*Hun Bol, Sajna Ki Aavan Kol?* 

*Kinu Poochan Main?*
*Ehsaas Kithe Rakhde Ne?*
Gallan Taalde Te Naal
*Kiven Hassde Ne?* 

Chhad Ditti Main Umeedan
*Saari Duniya Ton,*
Aiwein Lokan Diyan
*Gallan ‘Ch Phasde Ne.* 

Nahi Boldiyan Jhooth
*Nahi Main Nahi Boldiyan Jhooth,*
*Mere Te Tera Ae Suroor.*
*Tere Utte Likhan Geet,*
*Sone Jachde Ne.* 

*Dilan Di Yaari Saadi,*
*Ve Dilan Da Nahi Ae Kasoor.*
*Naal Rehna Si Zaroor,*
*Saade Thalle Iraade.* 

*Mera Koi Hor Nahi Ae,*
*Dass Ditta Duniya Nu.*
*Jadon Vi Aave,*
*Apne Naal Lave Khushiyan Nu.* 

*Jadon Vi Door Jaave,*
*Jaan Saadi Kad Jaave.*
*Sajna Ae Tere Kol,*
*Vasna Ae Chaave.* 

Teri Zimmedari
*Muskura Ke Le Layi Ae,*
*Saadi Zimmedari.*
*Main Nahi Kitti Kadi Vi,*
*Tere Ton Badgumani.* 

*Tu Mera Yaar Si,*
*Dil Aasman Paar Si.*
*Eh Do Dilan Da Pyaar Si O,*
*Pyaar Na Si Kaghazi Par.* 

*Meri Khwahish Ae Tu,*
*Meri Hasrat Ae Tu.*
*Assi Tere Utte Marde Ne,*
*Mande Nai Kyun.* 

*Hun Te Roz Tenu Chaahde Chaahde,*
*Tere Husn Utte Marde.*
*Assi Roz Ki Kariye, Sajna Bol?* 

*Haan, Tere Hi Jhol Utte Nachde Saare,*
*Tere Pyaar ‘Ch Kariye Ki?*
*Hun Bol, Sajna Ki Aavan Kol?* 

*Tere Te Main Waari Jawan,*
*Tere Gun Gawaan Main.*
*Tere Bin Jee Lagda Nahi Ae,*
*Bas Tenu Chawaan Main.* 

*Hun Raavan Mor,*
Hun Te Roz Tenu Chande Jande
Tere Husn Ute Marde Asi Roz
*Asi Roz Ki Kariye, Sajna Bol?* 

*Haan, Tere Hi Jhol Utte Nachde Saare,*
*Tere Pyaar ‘Ch Kariye Ki?*
*Hun Bol, Sajna Ki Aavan Kol?*
